1
00:00:06,570 --> 00:00:11,950
♪Obsessions penned
into an everlasting love♪

2
00:00:12,330 --> 00:00:17,580
♪Affections gently linger
around fingertips♪

3
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:23,140
♪May stars guide us through rough waves♪

4
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:28,520
♪I give all my love unreservedly♪

5
00:00:29,030 --> 00:00:30,900
♪May transient frost♪

6
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,690
♪Persist through obstacles for love♪

7
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:40,330
♪I wait for you to look back
in this rocky life♪

8
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:42,550
♪I can stay for the promise♪

9
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:46,180
♪Despite seasons recur♪

10
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:51,760
♪The love deep within
will transcend time♪

11
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:57,500
[Secrets of the Shadow Sect]

12
00:00:57,540 --> 00:01:00,820
[Episode 12]

13
00:01:44,380 --> 00:01:45,180
Darling.

14
00:01:45,940 --> 00:01:47,100
What is all this for?

15
00:01:47,700 --> 00:01:50,300
It's just a manual.

16
00:01:50,300 --> 00:01:52,180
Why can't you give it to me?

17
00:01:53,620 --> 00:01:54,940
Back then,

18
00:01:56,220 --> 00:01:58,100
when my master passed away,

19
00:01:58,100 --> 00:02:00,140
I thought he fell into a demonic path

20
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:02,540
while practicing the Wanxin Manual.

21
00:02:04,140 --> 00:02:05,860
But now it appeared

22
00:02:06,620 --> 00:02:09,180
you might have had a hand in it.

23
00:02:09,860 --> 00:02:11,460
Over the past two years,

24
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:14,260
many sects were slaughtered,

25
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:17,340
and their manuals went missing.

26
00:02:17,700 --> 00:02:20,780
You must be behind all this.

27
00:02:23,780 --> 00:02:25,660
Watch your mouth.

28
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:32,260
Ling Yuanzheng.

29
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:34,540
You have never been sincere to me.

30
00:02:36,060 --> 00:02:37,940
You are sanctimonious.

31
00:02:38,420 --> 00:02:40,700
Stop pretending.

32
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:45,660
Xiao Wenqing.

33
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:47,820
You broke all your meridians.

34
00:02:47,820 --> 00:02:49,180
I did!

35
00:02:49,780 --> 00:02:51,540
Should I wait for Yu to drug me

36
00:02:51,540 --> 00:02:53,620
and make me reveal the Wanxin Manual

37
00:02:53,620 --> 00:02:56,100
after losing all my rationalities?

38
00:02:56,420 --> 00:02:58,260
Ling Yuanzheng.

39
00:02:58,860 --> 00:03:00,700
In your dreams!

40
00:03:00,980 --> 00:03:03,300
Don't think for a second
you can use the Wanxin Manual

41
00:03:03,940 --> 00:03:06,180
to rule the entire martial arts world.

42
00:03:09,740 --> 00:03:11,580
Mother.

43
00:03:14,380 --> 00:03:15,700
I have been waiting for years.

44
00:03:16,980 --> 00:03:18,660
This day has finally come.

45
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:17,780
If I don't come out after an hour

46
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:20,460
and Yingshi hasn't killed Chiye...

47
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:21,620
If you don't come out,

48
00:04:22,060 --> 00:04:23,580
we won't retreat even in death.

49
00:05:04,060 --> 00:05:07,060
Rong searched for
the most excellent material

50
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:08,900
and hired the most well-known swordsmith
in the martial arts world

51
00:05:08,900 --> 00:05:09,940
to forge this dagger.

52
00:05:10,620 --> 00:05:12,260
Rong has put in a lot of effort

53
00:05:12,620 --> 00:05:14,300
to prepare your birthday gift

54
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:15,940
for the past few months.

55
00:05:19,020 --> 00:05:20,220
I really appreciate that, Rong.

56
00:05:20,700 --> 00:05:22,380
What a rare scene at your birthday.
Father.

57
00:05:25,780 --> 00:05:26,580
Xuan, you are here.

58
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:27,900
Xuan.

59
00:05:32,460 --> 00:05:34,900
It has been many years

60
00:05:35,020 --> 00:05:36,940
since I saw a happy family.

61
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:40,180
Over the years,

62
00:05:40,420 --> 00:05:42,420
the expenses I spent on my male escorts

63
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:43,620
has been high.

64
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:44,900
I couldn't afford

65
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:46,660
a valuable gift like Rong's.

66
00:05:46,900 --> 00:05:48,020
I only have this jar of liquor

67
00:05:48,220 --> 00:05:49,220
for you

68
00:05:49,220 --> 00:05:50,500
as my well wishes.

69
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:53,900
Today is your father's
fiftieth birthday.

70
00:05:54,020 --> 00:05:55,300
You just brought a jar of liquor

71
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:56,940
on such a big day.

72
00:05:59,020 --> 00:06:00,500
Today is a family gathering.

73
00:06:00,660 --> 00:06:02,100
There is no need
for so many formalities.

74
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:04,700
Xuan.

75
00:06:05,340 --> 00:06:08,180
You do have something

76
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:10,660
I have always wanted.

77
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:13,020
If you love me as your father,

78
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:15,980
can you present it

79
00:06:16,660 --> 00:06:18,500
as my birthday gift?

80
00:06:19,460 --> 00:06:20,740
What do you want, Father?

81
00:06:22,340 --> 00:06:23,860
Have you heard about the Wanxin Manual

82
00:06:24,220 --> 00:06:25,900
from your mother?

83
00:06:27,700 --> 00:06:28,500
No rush.

84
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:31,100
Before you demand for the Wanxin Manual,

85
00:06:31,580 --> 00:06:32,820
please allow me

86
00:06:33,180 --> 00:06:35,060
to give you a toast.

87
00:06:35,620 --> 00:06:36,500
Sure.

88
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:37,740
Come.

89
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:48,970
[Shadow Sect]

90
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:00,180
Yingshi.

91
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:05,140
What are you doing here

92
00:07:05,780 --> 00:07:07,100
instead of doing your mission?

93
00:07:07,980 --> 00:07:09,300
I, First Class shadow guard,

94
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:10,740
would like to challenge your position

95
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:13,500
to a life-and-death trial

96
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:15,060
according to the rules of
the Shadow Sect.

97
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:16,780
Yingshi.

98
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:17,700
Are you out of your mind?

99
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:22,660
What did you say?

100
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:26,820
I, First Class shadow guard,

101
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:29,780
would like to challenge your position

102
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:31,540
to a life-and-death trial.

103
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:34,540
He wants to challenge Mr. Chiye?

104
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:36,340
Does he want to seek death?

105
00:07:38,140 --> 00:07:38,940
Yingshi.

106
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:43,300
How dare you betray your master.

107
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:46,900
Surely, you jest.

108
00:07:47,340 --> 00:07:48,340
My master?

109
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:50,820
There has always been only one.

110
00:07:51,340 --> 00:07:52,260
Scoundrel.

111
00:07:55,460 --> 00:07:57,980
I should have noticed this.

112
00:07:58,740 --> 00:07:59,540
Fine.

113
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:02,220
Since you have a death wish,

114
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:04,700
I will grant it.

115
00:08:06,300 --> 00:08:08,900
According to the rules of
the Shadow Sect,

116
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:11,220
I accept Yingshi's challenge.

117
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:13,260
The winner lives,

118
00:08:14,060 --> 00:08:15,260
and the loser dies.

119
00:08:24,580 --> 00:08:26,980
You tested my internal energy
several times before

120
00:08:27,460 --> 00:08:28,740
because of this, right?

121
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:32,540
The first cup of liquor

122
00:08:33,020 --> 00:08:34,180
is for you, Father.

123
00:08:35,420 --> 00:08:38,060
You have endured

124
00:08:38,060 --> 00:08:39,340
for the past twenty years.

125
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:41,140
For the sake of the Wanxin Manual,

126
00:08:41,380 --> 00:08:43,460
you deceived my mother

127
00:08:44,020 --> 00:08:45,180
into breaking ties with the Feiyun Sect

128
00:08:45,180 --> 00:08:46,620
as the only disciple

129
00:08:46,700 --> 00:08:47,820
to his master

130
00:08:47,820 --> 00:08:49,300
and marrying into the Lingtian Palace.

131
00:08:51,020 --> 00:08:51,820
Father.

132
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:53,860
You used yourself as the bait

133
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:56,220
in your own scheme.

134
00:08:57,220 --> 00:08:58,980
It must have been tough for you
over the years.

135
00:08:59,820 --> 00:09:01,020
What are you on about?

136
00:09:03,100 --> 00:09:04,540
Calm down, Father.

137
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:07,180
You orchestrated everything for years
to obtain the Wanxin Manual.

138
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:08,820
Now, the banquet has started.

139
00:09:09,220 --> 00:09:10,740
You should be more patient.

140
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:12,620
Let me give my toast first.

141
00:09:12,940 --> 00:09:13,980
Then, I will present you

142
00:09:14,340 --> 00:09:16,020
the Wanxin Manual.

143
00:09:22,380 --> 00:09:24,940
Impressive, my dear daughter.

144
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:27,140
Good.

145
00:09:27,900 --> 00:09:28,420
Very good.

146
00:09:29,940 --> 00:09:31,740
I would like to hear

147
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:33,020
what else

148
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:35,860
you are going to say next.

149
00:09:40,380 --> 00:09:43,700
♪If hand waves are
the prelude to farewell♪

150
00:09:44,140 --> 00:09:47,300
♪If words hold no intention to stall♪

151
00:09:47,860 --> 00:09:49,580
♪Goodbye♪

152
00:09:49,780 --> 00:09:53,620
♪Should be reserved
for when our lives are at stake♪

153
00:09:54,900 --> 00:09:58,230
♪If time rushes swiftly
like wind and dust♪

154
00:09:58,620 --> 00:10:01,940
♪If tears come before words
after waking up♪

155
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:04,620
♪May you not be drowned in bitterness♪

156
00:10:04,940 --> 00:10:06,220
♪I only wish your eyes♪

157
00:10:06,380 --> 00:10:09,300
♪As pure as snow♪
